decks.notes: The deck focuses on combining various artifacts and creatures to create powerful synergies and win the game. It includes cards like Helm of Obedience and Grindstone to mill opponents' libraries, while also incorporating combos like March of Otherworldly Light and Pyre of Heroes to generate value and search for key pieces. The deck also includes disruptive elements, such as Winter Orb and Tangle Wire, to slow down opponents and gain an advantage. It utilizes cards like Umezawa's Jitte and Stoneforge Mystic to provide strong creature support and control the board. Overall, the deck aims to assemble its combo pieces while maintaining control and disrupting opponents' strategies.
